
= ILMN

URL =


=Description=

"Working people throughout the globe face attack on their basic economic and social rights and the need to tell the stories of all working people is crucial in building solidarity and education. Privatization, deregulation and the attack on health and safety along with the living conditions of all working people are issues in every country. The International Labor Media Network ILMN was established to use streaming and the internet to get our stories to workers throughout the world. We invite your union and worker communication organization to stream your press conference, education meeting or actions on this multi-media internatonal labor platform. Contact us if you want to be a partner and would like to get your stories out."


